## 📱 Mobile Client Tips (For a Perfect Full-Screen Layout)
To prevent vertical text stretching or cropping on modern long phone screens:
1. Open the side menu in your mobile **Chrome Remote Desktop** app.
2. **Disable** "Resize desktop to fit".
3. **Enable** "Scale to fit" or "Fit to screen".
4. **Best Experience:** Turn on screen rotation on your phone and hold it in **Landscape (Horizontal)** mode. You will see a perfect, uncropped, 1:1 full-screen mirror of your active external display with crisp text!

