## 🌟 Key Advantages: Why This Solution is Safe & Robust
* **No Root System Modification:** All configurations reside completely inside your user's home directory (`~`). It is fully immune to system updates and will never break the OS.
* **Self-Healing:** If any connection abruptly drops or freezes, systemd immediately detects it and restarts the bridge cleanly in the background.
* **Set and Forget:** The bridge starts automatically on system boot. There is no need to manually open Google Chrome or run terminal commands ever again!
